{"tid":8111,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人有養鸚鵡","createTime":"2016-11-28T07:07:51.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-12T02:47:12.000Z","uid":8103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1dbc6cdf49829eb16dfe924fe484da9a3fc6828c","tid":8111,"uid":8103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T07:07:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z9gE0B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz9gE0B.jpg&h=2665f7f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n企係度訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢隻唔比我掂<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yYvx2S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyYvx2S.jpg&h=df6ffc86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢隻黎左冇耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比摸摸但都係好驚人"},{"pid":"e9aa3e7280df9cb3fd31ed1e4530e24195e102b0","tid":8111,"uid":30171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T07:10:39.000Z","msg":"藍色果隻好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都好鍾意鸚鵡，覺得佢地好醒又得意"},{"pid":"05ce78b975bdd8960e0eb73bb2ba046627eec400","tid":8111,"uid":30377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T07:11:58.000Z","msg":"呢啲通常邊到入手？同埋幾錢左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1897472909e744b35b74ce03106086d06753cbb9","tid":8111,"uid":8103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T07:21:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>藍色果隻好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都好鍾意鸚鵡，覺得佢地好醒又得意</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我呢兩隻品種都唔係醒個批<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n太聰明我唔敢養 驚陪佢地唔夠會抑鬱"},{"pid":"37760a88b5fe59177c9467426d3ef65e4fcd6a45","tid":8111,"uid":8103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T07:23:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢啲通常邊到入手？同埋幾錢左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係雀仔街買咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都係新手上路<br />\n雞尾（第一隻）500左右<br />\n愛情鳥200左右有一隻，不過我呢隻叫白面愛情鳥，要900<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05bbf7a564ed833163d809090f08633f5f5107af","tid":8111,"uid":8103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T07:29:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/24ht63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F24ht63.jpg&h=586d419c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n痴狗多過痴人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"230e5ee3ff3473149b12042abc8fa790ad7acc40","tid":8111,"uid":47649,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T17:52:25.000Z","msg":"玄鳳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/01/015206_a52d0548f4d415d98c8386029d0c8eaf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F01%2F015206_a52d0548f4d415d98c8386029d0c8eaf.jpg&h=dac067cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"16a23814dfa6987f2b9cb209f6ff5a8b252271dc","tid":8111,"uid":8103,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T05:51:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玄鳳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/01/015206_a52d0548f4d415d98c8386029d0c8eaf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg